{"id": 39, "genre": 1000, "title": "好莱坞电影，你看不看配音版？", "description": "新上映的《驯龙高手2》有原版和配音版两种可以看，配音版是林更新、白百合和蒋雯丽配的哟，这个组合听着有点怪，但据说还不错。那……你平时看原版还是配音版？\r\n", "record_count": 3873, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": null, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606161908y7FtAeaHroJ3IYM8.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-08-14T17:12:35Z", "questions": [{"id": 58, "title": "好莱坞电影，你看不看配音版？", "content": "看电影，你看不看配音版？", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 526, "content": "看配音版，因为我要带小孩去看", "image": "img/option/option/2016060616173503BWVJ5IgqXmeL8F.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 527, "content": "看配音版，因为看字幕太累", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161735HezTqDGQYaniK4oh.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 528, "content": "看配音版，如果配音演员里有我喜欢的明星的话", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161735S8JhpQd2TmktVXoi.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 529, "content": "看配音版，我觉得配音腔很有趣", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161735NsLRXPuqkIWOg4DC.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 530, "content": "不看配音版，好莱坞电影就应该原汁原味", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161736Du4TWzlqFcS38iLx.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 531, "content": "不看配音版，现在的翻译太差，我都靠自己听", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161736dk0FmNOLB5Ifvty1.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 532, "content": "不看配音版，现在的配音演员太差", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161736AjItfGJNpaq2rCeF.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 533, "content": "不看配音版，不知道为什么我就是觉得违和", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161736CqntpDmcOE1PW0S6.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}